data.title: Third District Court of Appeal
data.text:
Note: Opinions are not final until any timely filed motions for rehearing are considered and disposed of by the Court. These opinions are also subject to revision before publication in the Southern Reporter, 3rd Series.

The court releases its opinions to the parties and public each Wednesday.

In emergency and expedited matters, the court releases its opinions at such other times as may be ordered by the court.

To view opinions, you must have Acrobat Reader installed.
